subject: Sony Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Martina Hingis won her first doubles title since 2007 as she and Sabine Lisicki defeated Ekaterina Makarova and Elena Vesnina, 4-6, 6-4, 10-5, at the Sony Open in Key Biscayne, Fla.
